headline: Beyond Meat Stock Is on a Wild Ride. Why a Meme Rally Looks Undercooked.
summary: Beyond Meat  has become more than a hot take for retail investors and short sellers chasing the next meme stock.  Before then, Beyond Meat may struggle to get its products in the hands of customers—despite recent efforts to expand its presence in grocery stores across the U.S. Earlier this week, the company announced it was expanding an existing partnership with  Walmart  and introduced a new partnership with high-end grocer Erewhon.
